ValueSet: AicuraRaceEthnicityVS
Id: aicura-race-ethnicity
Title: "AICURA Race & Ethnicity ValueSet"
Description: "Race and ethnicity concepts from the US CDC Race & Ethnicity code system, as used in AICURA patient demographics. The source code system mixes race and ethnicity concepts under a single OID, so a single combined value set is bound to both the race and ethnicity extensions."
* ^experimental = false
* include codes from system AicuraRaceEthnicityCS
